---
source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Save page as PDF

Usage: bl pdf [OPTIONS] [url]

Arguments:
  [url]  URL to navigate to before saving

Options:
  -o, --output <output>  Output file path [default: page.pdf]
  -v, --verbose          Enable debug logging
      --headless         Hide browser window (visible by default)
      --json             Output as JSON
  -h, --help             Print help

Examples:
  bl pdf -o page.pdf
  # Save current page as PDF

  bl pdf https://example.com -o page.pdf
  # Navigate to URL first, then save as PDF
